      "suggestion": "Ensure strict adherence to networking layer terminology and keep SerDes/OSFP terms in English where appropriate."
    },
    {
      "location": "Thermal/Power Delivery",
      "issue": "Transition between mechanical units (mm, microns) and electrical units (VDC, Amps).",
      "suggestion": "Maintain precision in units and use standard Chinese engineering terms for 'step-down' (降压) and 'busbar' (母线)."
    },
    {
      "location": "Groq Section",
      "issue": "Nuance between 'acquisition' and 'licensing agreement'.",
